description:
If you want to apply for Eleven's last investment round but you still have questions or doubts, this event is right for you!

All teams from Varna are welcome to meet Dimitar Georgiev, founder of Gym Realm and Eleven Ambassador, this Friday (Feb 20th) at 7 pm in http://varnalab.org/.

As an Eleven alumni, Dimitar will tell you all you want to know about our:
- selection process;
- investment terms;
- accelerator program;
- network, community and more.

The meetup is informal, over beers, and open for everyone.
